---
title: Smokey Beef Meatballs & Tomato Sauce with Garlic Rice & Yoghurt
description: Discover a fusion of North African-style flavours with a whole new twist! Take tasty garlic rice piled with moreish beef meatballs, all
the right spices and tender veggies, and you’ve got a dinner-time hit. Serve with yoghurt for the ultimate creamy, cooling effect.
